            . I am a <rs id="t18180218-157-viclabel830" type="occupation">waiter at the King's Head, Old-change</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-157-victim975 t18180218-157-viclabel830"></join>. On the 1st of February, I employed the prisoner to clean shoes-the articles stated in the indictment, where in the place where he was. I went out, and met him with a bundle; I did not suspect him - I returned and missed the things. I met him again, and charged him with stealing them - He ran off, I followed, and secured him.</p>
